text: This is a list of female scientists from Oceania. ==Australia== :Pages appear in :Category:Australian scientists *Elizabeth Blackburn *Gretta Pecl, marine biologist *Helen Quinn, physicist *Halina Rubinsztein-Dunlop, physicist *Fiona Stanley, studies epidemiology and health *Donna Strickland, won the 2018 Nobel Prize in physics *Penny Whetton, climate scientist, d. 2019 *Jeannette Young, physician, former health minister, and politician ==Cook Islands== * Jacqueline Evans, marine conservationist; has a Goldman Environmental Prize ==New Zealand== *Nancy Adams, got the awards, Queen's Service Order, and the New Zealand 1990 Commemoration Medal.
